Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:11.64,staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(874,300)}{\blur5\fad(500,500)}翻 譯     神棍蛙    澄     {\fs36}89
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 聽說過沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 第四真祖？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.78,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz10\move(740,430,500,500)}或者說是「焰光夜伯」　Kaleido Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說呢 第四名真祖…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.62,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,640)\frz352\fs90}{\k40}在{\k40}哪{\k40}裡{\k40}？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用問 就在這個城市裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人乃為不死不滅之身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:26.33,staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(236,510)}{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校 對         貓醬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有血族同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.08,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,540)\frz-8\fs72}{\k60}不渴望{\k30}去{\k20}支{\k20}配
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:28.08,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(890,280)\frz-8\fs72}不滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不渴望去支配
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是駕馭著災禍的化身十二眷獸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:31.67,staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,260)}{\blur5\fad(500,500)}時 間         山風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:35.93,staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(905,526)}{\blur5\fad(500,500)}後 期         翻毛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙不會被任何人支配
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是脫離了世間拘束 冷酷無情的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢…然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然…然後就沒有然後了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼故事嘛 一點都不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起你那故事 你覺得我這浴衣怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…太一般了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不知道把這穿上去有多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭… 涼鞋的繫帶還斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是木履的屐帶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可怎麼辦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法…來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭…就這模樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死…饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}也沒什麼吧 又不遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}真色情
